other centrally-acting alpha-2 agonists has not been established.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/85079/', '', 'Amphetamine, Pemoline, Atomoxetine, Metamfetamine, Lisdexamfetamine, Solriamfetol, Caffeine, Dextroamphetamine, Armodafinil, Citicoline, Modafinil', '', 1767369485);
